Title: Thymeleaf live reload with npm scripts
Description:
In my book Taming Thymeleaf I use Gulp to setup the frontend build pipeline and have live reloading during development.
For the workshop I gave at Spring I/O 2022 Barcelona, I used a different approach using NPM scripts.
This avoids the extra gulp dependency with sometimes things that are not up-to-date anymore.
